{"words":[{"word":"petals","count":5},{"word":"augusta","count":2},{"word":"wish","count":2},{"word":"rosebearer","count":2},{"word":"yes","count":2},{"word":"celebration","count":2},{"word":"chosen","count":2},{"word":"people","count":2},{"word":"side","count":2},{"word":"rain","count":2},{"word":"bruno","count":1},{"word":"master","count":1},{"word":"ceremonies","count":1},{"word":"occasion","count":1},{"word":"hoped","count":1},{"word":"greet","count":1},{"word":"alongside","count":1},{"word":"called","count":1},{"word":"away","count":1},{"word":"senate","count":1},{"word":"insists","count":1},{"word":"wasting","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"trifles","count":1},{"word":"bestow","count":1},{"word":"upon","count":1},{"word":"honor","count":1},{"word":"roses","count":1},{"word":"symbolize","count":1},{"word":"glory","count":1},{"word":"triumph","count":1},{"word":"shared","count":1},{"word":"gathered","count":1},{"word":"ceremonial","count":1},{"word":"role","count":1},{"word":"worry","count":1},{"word":"pretty","count":1},{"word":"simple","count":1},{"word":"handing","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"height","count":1},{"word":"everyone","count":1},{"word":"toss","count":1},{"word":"into","count":1},{"word":"air","count":1},{"word":"shower","count":1},{"word":"flowers","count":1},{"word":"task","count":1},{"word":"distribute","count":1},{"word":"beforehand","count":1},{"word":"held","count":1},{"word":"highest","count":1},{"word":"regard","count":1},{"word":"septimont","count":1},{"word":"gave","count":1},{"word":"battlefield","count":1},{"word":"fighting","count":1},{"word":"share","count":1},{"word":"honey","count":1},{"word":"wine","count":1},{"word":"beneath","count":1},{"word":"first","count":1},{"word":"non-local","count":1},{"word":"believe","count":1},{"word":"already","count":1},{"word":"moment","count":1},{"word":"cut","count":1},{"word":"dark","count":1},{"word":"tide's","count":1},{"word":"miasma","count":1},{"word":"without","count":1},{"word":"sovereign's","count":1},{"word":"defeat","count":1},{"word":"possible","count":1},{"word":"oh","count":1},{"word":"hope","count":1},{"word":"decline","count":1},{"word":"augusta's","count":1},{"word":"people's","count":1},{"word":"arrives","count":1},{"word":"join","count":1},{"word":"rosebearers","count":1},{"word":"sure","count":1},{"word":"partook","count":1},{"word":"hunt","count":1},{"word":"honored","count":1},{"word":"receive","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"leave","count":1},{"word":"capable","count":1},{"word":"hands","count":1},{"word":"choose","count":1},{"word":"trust","count":1},{"word":"instincts","count":1},{"word":"toast","count":1},{"word":"priestess's","count":1},{"word":"oration","count":1},{"word":"part","count":1},{"word":"overthink","count":1},{"word":"enjoy","count":1},{"word":"triumphant","count":1},{"word":"grander","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"I am Bruno, Master of Ceremonies for the occasion. I had hoped to greet you alongside Augusta.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"But she was called away... The Senate insists on wasting her time with their trifles.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"We wish to bestow upon you the honor of Rosebearer. Roses symbolize our glory and triumph, to be shared with all who are gathered here.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Yes, it's a ceremonial role. Don't worry, it's pretty simple, and you won't be handing out too many.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"At the height of the celebration, everyone will toss their petals into the air. We will all shower in the flowers.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Your task will be to distribute the petals beforehand. You have been chosen by the people, for you are held in the highest regard.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"The people of Septimont gave their all on the battlefield. Now, after fighting side by side, we'll share honey and wine beneath a rain of petals.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"You are our first non-local Rosebearer. But I believe you were already chosen the moment you cut through the Dark Tide's miasma. Without you, the Sovereign's defeat would not have been possible.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Yes... Oh, I hope you won't decline. This is not only Augusta's wish, it's the people's too.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"When Augusta arrives, she'll join the other Rosebearers. I'm sure those who partook in the hunt will be honored to receive petals from you.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Very well, I'll leave it in your capable hands.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"As for who you choose and how, trust your instincts. It's just like a toast, or a Priestess's oration, all part of the celebration. No need to overthink it. Now, enjoy!","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Come, triumphant rain of petals...","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Make it even grander...","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001}]}